OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773846665
OL,3,CBodycam footage shows Walsall killer
OL,4,Cfather being handcuffed by officers
OL,6,FCredit: Staffordshire Police
OL,8,FThis is the moment a killer father
OL,9,Fthreatened to report two police
OL,10,Fofficers after his "hand was hurt" as
OL,11,Fhe was put in handcuffs.
OL,13,FNew footage shows Sean Jefferson, who
OL,14,Fwas found guilty of the murder of his
OL,15,Ffive-week-old daughter earlier this
OL,16,Fweek, accusing an officer of
OL,17,F"squeezing" the cuffs.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
