PN,37402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773846665
OL,3,CBodycam footage shows Walsall killer
OL,4,Cfather being handcuffed by officers
OL,6,FHe was told to "calm down" as he got
OL,7,Fincreasingly agitated, as he was
OL,8,Farrested over the violent abuse he
OL,9,Fsubjected young Darcy to.
OL,11,FJefferson, 35, called 999 on March 27,
OL,12,F2022, telling the operator his baby
OL,13,Fhad 'stopped breathing'. Sadly, Darcy
OL,14,F- who had suffered a catastrophic head
OL,15,Finjury - died in hospital on March 29.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773846665
OL,3,CBodycam footage shows Walsall killer
OL,4,Cfather being handcuffed by officers
OL,6,FThroughout her short life, Darcy had
OL,7,Fbeen repeatedly assaulted and had
OL,8,Fsustained 47 rib fractures. Both her
OL,9,Flegs were also fractured - and these
OL,10,Fwere not the only injuries cruelly
OL,11,Finflicted on Darcy.
OL,13,FWhen Jefferson and Darcy's mother, Amy
OL,14,FLeigh Clark were arrested on suspicion
OL,15,Fof murder, the killer dad said: "Oh my
OL,16,F******* god."
OL,18,FHe covered his face with his hand and
OL,19,Fthen seemed to shake his head in
OL,20,Fdisbelief - as can be viewed in the
OL,21,Fvideo above.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
