PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773846665
OL,3,CBodycam footage shows Walsall killer
OL,4,Cfather being handcuffed by officers
OL,6,FFurther footage shows the pair being
OL,7,Farrested again in light of "new
OL,8,Fevidence". As he's cuffed, an
OL,9,Fincreasingly annoyed Jefferson says:
OL,10,F"That's a bit tight, that is mate.
OL,11,FLook at that, see that?
OL,13,F"That's very tight. Can you please
OL,14,Floose it?"
OL,16,FThe officer tells him to "stay still
OL,17,Fthen", only for Jefferson to demand
OL,18,Fhis badge number and say: "I'm putting
OL,19,Fin a complaint about you. Simple,
OL,20,Fdone."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773846665
OL,3,CBodycam footage shows Walsall killer
OL,4,Cfather being handcuffed by officers
OL,6,FJefferson continues: "You're hurting
OL,7,Fmy hand, mate."
OL,9,FHe's told to "calm down", as he
OL,10,Fdemands: "Take it off then, hurry up."
OL,12,F"I want your name and badge number,
OL,13,Fyou're abusing your rights now, mate.
OL,14,FSimple."
OL,16,FAnother officer explains he was
OL,17,Fgetting the key to loosen the cuffs,
OL,18,Fonly to be told: "I'm gonna report you
OL,19,Fas well."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
