OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773846665
OL,3,CBodycam footage shows Walsall killer
OL,4,Cfather being handcuffed by officers
OL,6,FHis voice gets louder as he says:
OL,7,F"You're squeezing them, geezer."
OL,9,FThe other officer says: "He isn't
OL,10,Fsqueezing them. They've been locked,
OL,11,Fthey're not going to get any tighter."
OL,13,FJefferson, from Walsall, was found
OL,14,Fguilty of murder, at Stafford Crown
OL,15,FCourt on Monday, March 16, following
OL,16,Fan eight-week trial.
OL,18,FHe was also found guilty of causing/
OL,19,Fallowing the death of a child and two
OL,20,Fcounts of Section 18 - grievous bodily
OL,21,Fharm with intent.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
