PN,37407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773846665
OL,3,CBodycam footage shows Walsall killer
OL,4,Cfather being handcuffed by officers
OL,6,FClark, 34, of Lichfield, was found
OL,7,Fguilty of causing/allowing the death
OL,8,Fof a child and two counts of causing
OL,9,For allowing serious harm to a child
OL,10,Fafter charges of murder or
OL,11,Fmanslaughter against her were dropped
OL,12,Fby prosecutors as closing speeches
OL,13,Fwere made to the court last week.
OL,15,FBoth parents were taking drugs during
OL,16,Ftheir daughter's short life, the trial
OL,17,Fwas told.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/10
