CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773846665
OL,3,CBodycam footage shows Walsall killer
OL,4,Cfather being handcuffed by officers
OL,6,FProsecution counsel Harpreet Sandhu KC
OL,7,Fsaid the head injury had been caused
OL,8,Fby Darcy being shaken violently or
OL,9,Fhaving her head struck against a
OL,10,Fsurface at their then-home in
OL,11,FBurntwood.
OL,13,FFollowing the verdict, Detective Chief
OL,14,FInspector Ian Fitzgerald, from
OL,15,FStaffordshire Police's Major
OL,16,FInvestigations Department, said: "The
OL,17,Fverdict concludes a profoundly
OL,18,Fdistressing case involving the murder
OL,19,Fof five-week-old Darcy.
OL,26,@xD@bOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/10
