PN,37409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773846665
OL,3,CBodycam footage shows Walsall killer
OL,4,Cfather being handcuffed by officers
OL,6,F"Her short life and tragic death must
OL,7,Fnot be forgotten. Darcy was violently
OL,8,Fabused and murdered by her father. Her
OL,9,Fmother allowed her death.
OL,11,F"These were the people who should have
OL,12,Floved and cared for her. It was
OL,13,Fdespicable behaviour against a
OL,14,Fdefenceless child.
OL,16,F"It has been an exceptionally
OL,17,Fdifficult investigation and the
OL,18,Fthoughts of the entire investigation
OL,19,Fteam remain with her elder sibling,
OL,20,Fwho has faced an unimaginable loss and
OL,21,Fa lengthy judicial process."
OL,26,@xD@AOU
